OL,3,CSuspended chief constable paid nine
OL,4,Cmonths' salary to retire
OL,6,FThe suspended chief constable of Devon
OL,7,Fand Cornwall Police Will Kerr was paid
OL,8,Fthe equivalent of nine months' salary
OL,9,Fto retire, it has emerged.
OL,11,FIn July, Mr Kerr, who has not been
OL,12,Farrested or charged with any offence,
OL,13,Fannounced he had chosen to retire,
OL,14,Fstating it was in the "best interests"
OL,15,Fof his family and the force.
OL,17,FNow Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,18,FAlison Hernandez confirmed the former
OL,19,Fchief received a settlement of
OL,20,F#165,539.
