OL,3,CSuspended chief constable paid nine
OL,4,Cmonths' salary to retire
OL,6,FMr Kerr was suspended in July 2023 by
OL,7,Fthe Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,8,Ffollowing a mandatory referral to the
OL,9,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct.
OL,11,FHad he not retired, he would have
OL,12,Fcontinued to receive his usual monthly
OL,13,Fwage because the investigation into
OL,14,Fgross misconduct remains ongoing, with
OL,15,Fno certainty when it will conclude.
