OL,3,CSuspended chief constable paid nine
OL,4,Cmonths' salary to retire
OL,6,FHis contract was due to run until
OL,7,FDecember 2027, meaning taxpayers could
OL,8,Fhave been funding the salary of a
OL,9,Fsuspended chief constable for 29
OL,10,Fmonths had a settlement not been
OL,11,Freached.
OL,13,FCommissioner Hernandez has since
OL,14,Fannounced that Interim Chief Constable
OL,15,FJames Vaughan has agreed to remain in
OL,16,Fpost until January 2027.
OL,18,FShe said it would bring stability to
OL,19,FDevon and Cornwall Police which would
OL,20,Fnot have been possible had Mr Kerr
OL,21,Fremained suspended.
