OL,6,FNow confirming the details of Mr
OL,7,FKerr's settlement terms, she said: "Mr
OL,8,FKerr was suspended on full pay from
OL,9,FJuly 2023 as per the requirements of
OL,10,Fpolice regulations while
OL,11,Finvestigations into his conduct
OL,12,Fcontinued.
OL,14,F"With no certainty on the length of
OL,15,Fthe IOPC investigation the reality we
OL,16,Fwere facing was significant additional
OL,17,Fcosts to taxpayers and continued
OL,18,Fleadership instability.
