OL,6,F"By reaching a financial settlement,
OL,7,Fthat uncertainty has now been resolved
OL,8,Fand efforts can now be fully focused
OL,9,Fon delivering a stable and effective
OL,10,Fpolice force."
OL,12,FThe Commissioner said she remained
OL,13,F"incredibly frustrated" by the length
OL,14,Fof time the ongoing investigation was
OL,15,Ftaking.
